These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, soy-milk, sprite
Sport: golf, basketball, badminton, rowing
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the right of Sport:badminton##1
2. Sport:rowing is on the far left##1
3. Sport:badminton is between Sport:basketball and Beverage:almond-milk##2
4. Beverage:sprite is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:soy-milk is between Beverage:almond-milk and Beverage:hot-chocolate##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | sprite         | almond-milk   | soy-milk | hot-chocolate       |
| Sport      | rowing | golf | badminton   | basketball |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: hiking, dancing, cooking, fishing
Nationality: canadian, german, italian, mexican
1. Nationality:mexican is between Hobby:cooking and Nationality:german##2
2. Hobby:fishing is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:italian is on the right of Nationality:canadian##1
4. Hobby:hiking is on the left of Nationality:canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | dancing | hiking | cooking | fishing |
| Nationality   | german    | mexican   | canadian | italian       |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
