2. Nationality:polish is between Nationality:italian and Food:grapes##2
3. Nationality:italian is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:dutch is on the left of Food:nectarine##1
5. Food:grapes == Nationality:dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | carrot    | onion | grapes   | nectarine  |
| Nationality   | italian | polish   | dutch | nigerian |

